                                        1208,
                                        1125
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " sequential integration steps) to cross, rendering this approach infeasible. To overcome this, prior work has produced an array of enhanced sampling methods, such as coarse graining (Clementi, 2008; Kmiecik et al., 2016) and metadynamics (Laio & Parrinello, 2002). However, these methods require domain knowledge specific to each molecular system to implement effectively."
                                }
